        {
            "title": "花旗策略師認為投資者將進一步分散配置、減少對美股的依賴",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg, MSCI, Citigroup\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"592\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Ftn04YZihCFaMeAruz78Yg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU5MjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/cd9dd16c0049d142c5e8caac25517e5b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg, MSCI, Citigroup</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 花旗集團策略師指出，2026年投資者將繼續加大對美國股票以外資產的配置多元化，這一趨勢將推動全球基準股票指數進一步上漲10%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由Beata Manthey領導的團隊在報告中寫道，關鍵原因在於美國與全球其他地區盈利水平的日益趨同。在歐洲政府支出、日本再通膨及人工智能廣泛應用的推動下，美國以外的關鍵市場仍有望實現每股純益改善。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">花旗團隊表示，「投資者目前對國際股票信心增強，當前全球其他地區相對於美國的持倉立場明顯更趨樂觀，整體風險偏好較一年前更為廣泛。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b9cccd4f-1190-34e0-9568-7649a840e516-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Manthey此前提出逆勢觀點，將歐洲大陸股票評級上調至超配。去年，斯托克600指數最終創下2021年以來最強勁的年度表現，以美元計價漲幅超越標普500指數。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"592\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/iiUyo61K2KVzdfOVFZUnMw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU5MjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/8ed295bae8d9a436fa5a6f17c785238d\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Manthey及其團隊預計MSCI AC World指數年底將收於1360點，較上周五收盤價高出約10%。該團隊指出，分散投資並不意味著明確拋售美國資產，花旗預測標普500指數在2026年將上漲11%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Citi’s Manthey Sees More Diversification Out of US Stocks (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Michael Msika.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8A%B1%E6%97%97%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5%E5%B8%AB%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%80%85%E5%B0%87%E9%80%B2-%E6%AD%A5%E5%88%86%E6%95%A3%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-%E6%B8%9B%E5%B0%91%E5%B0%8D%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%9D%E8%B3%B4-122953283.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-12 21:00:51",
